#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:12
msgid ""
"Toutes les réponses sur le fonctionnement du moteur EuroMillions, les "
"étoiles et le jeu responsable."
msgstr ""
"All the answers about how the EuroMillions engine works, stars and "
"responsible gambling."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:22
msgid ""
"Toutes les réponses sur le fonctionnement du moteur EuroMillions et le "
"jeu responsable."
msgstr ""
"All the answers about how the EuroMillions engine works and responsible "
"gambling."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:32 ui/templates/em/faq.html:249
msgid "Comment fonctionne le simulateur de grilles EuroMillions ?"
msgstr "How does the EuroMillions grid simulator work?"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:35
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Notre simulateur utilise le moteur HYBRIDE, un algorithme qui analyse "
"%(total)s+ tirages historiques de l'EuroMillions. Le système combine "
"analyse long terme et tendances récentes pour générer des grilles de 5 "
"numéros (1-50) et 2 étoiles (1-12)."
msgstr ""
"Our simulator uses the HYBRIDE engine, an algorithm that analyses "
"%(total)s+ historical EuroMillions draws. The system combines long-term "
"analysis and recent trends to generate grids of 5 numbers (1-50) and 2 "
"stars (1-12)."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:40 ui/templates/em/faq.html:260
msgid "Le EuroMillions est-il prévisible ?"
msgstr "Can EuroMillions results be predicted?"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:43
msgid ""
"NON. L'EuroMillions est un jeu de pur hasard. Probabilité de gagner le "
"jackpot : 1 sur 139 838 160. Notre outil est purement statistique et "
"descriptif."
msgstr ""
"NO. EuroMillions is a pure game of chance. The probability of winning the"
" jackpot is 1 in 139,838,160. Our tool is purely statistical and "
"descriptive."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:48 ui/templates/em/faq.html:291
msgid "Que signifient numéros chauds et froids ?"
msgstr "What do hot and cold numbers mean?"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:51
msgid ""
"Un numéro chaud est sorti fréquemment sur les 2 dernières années. Un "
"numéro froid est rarement sorti. L'analyse porte sur les 50 numéros "
"principaux ET les 12 étoiles."
msgstr ""
"A hot number has been drawn frequently over the last 2 years. A cold "
"number has rarely been drawn. The analysis covers all 50 main numbers AND"
" the 12 stars."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:56 ui/templates/em/faq.html:303
msgid "Comment sont calculées les étoiles ?"
msgstr "How are the stars calculated?"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:59
msgid ""
"Les 2 étoiles (1-12) sont analysées séparément avec leur propre "
"fréquence, écart et catégorie chaud/froid/neutre."
msgstr ""
"The 2 stars (1-12) are analysed separately with their own frequency, gap "
"and hot/cold/neutral category."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:64 ui/templates/em/faq.html:321
msgid "D'où viennent les données ?"
msgstr "Where does the data come from?"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:67
msgid ""
"Les données proviennent des tirages officiels de l'EuroMillions. La base "
"contient plusieurs années d'historique, mise à jour après chaque tirage "
"officiel (mardi et vendredi)."
msgstr ""
"The data comes from the official EuroMillions draws. The database "
"contains several years of history, updated after each official draw "
"(Tuesday and Friday)."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:228
msgid "Accès rapide"
msgstr "Quick access"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:230 ui/templates/em/faq.html:245
msgid "Fonctionnement"
msgstr "How it works"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:231 ui/templates/em/faq.html:287
msgid "Numéros et Étoiles"
msgstr "Numbers and Stars"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:232 ui/templates/em/faq.html:317
msgid "Données"
msgstr "Data"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:233 ui/templates/em/faq.html:346
msgid "Jeu Responsable"
msgstr "Responsible Gambling"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:253
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Notre simulateur utilise le <strong>moteur HYBRIDE</strong>, un "
"algorithme qui analyse <strong>%(total)s+ tirages historiques</strong> de"
" l'EuroMillions."
msgstr ""
"Our simulator uses the <strong>HYBRIDE engine</strong>, an algorithm that"
" analyses <strong>%(total)s+ historical draws</strong> from EuroMillions."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:254
msgid ""
"Le système combine analyse long terme et tendances récentes pour générer "
"des grilles de <strong>5 numéros (1-50)</strong> et <strong>2 étoiles "
"(1-12)</strong>."
msgstr ""
"The system combines long-term analysis and recent trends to generate "
"grids of <strong>5 numbers (1-50)</strong> and <strong>2 stars "
"(1-12)</strong>."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:264
msgid ""
"<strong>NON.</strong> L'EuroMillions est un jeu de pur hasard. Aucune "
"méthode, algorithme ou statistique ne peut prédire les résultats futurs."
msgstr ""
"<strong>NO.</strong> EuroMillions is a pure game of chance. No method, "
"algorithm or statistic can predict future results."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:265
msgid ""
"Notre outil est <strong>purement statistique et descriptif</strong>. Il "
"ne garantit AUCUN gain."
msgstr ""
"Our tool is <strong>purely statistical and descriptive</strong>. It "
"guarantees NO winnings whatsoever."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:266
msgid "<em>Probabilité de gagner le jackpot : 1 sur 139 838 160</em>"
msgstr "<em>Probability of winning the jackpot: 1 in 139,838,160</em>"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:272
msgid "Quelle est la différence avec le Loto ?"
msgstr "What is the difference compared to the French Loto?"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:276
msgid ""
"L'EuroMillions utilise <strong>5 numéros de 1 à 50 + 2 étoiles de 1 à "
"12</strong>, contre 5 numéros de 1 à 49 + 1 chance de 1 à 10 pour le "
"Loto."
msgstr ""
"EuroMillions uses <strong>5 numbers from 1 to 50 + 2 stars from 1 to "
"12</strong>, compared with 5 numbers from 1 to 49 + 1 lucky number from 1"
" to 10 for the French Loto."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:277
msgid ""
"Les tirages EuroMillions ont lieu les <strong>mardis et "
"vendredis</strong>, tandis que le Loto se joue les lundis, mercredis et "
"samedis."
msgstr ""
"EuroMillions draws take place on <strong>Tuesdays and Fridays</strong>, "
"whilst the French Loto is drawn on Mondays, Wednesdays and Saturdays."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:278
msgid ""
"Le moteur utilisé est <strong>HYBRIDE</strong>, une adaptation spécifique"
" du moteur HYBRIDE pour les règles EuroMillions."
msgstr ""
"The engine used is <strong>HYBRIDE</strong>, a version specifically "
"adapted for the EuroMillions rules."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:295
msgid ""
"Un <strong>numéro chaud</strong> est sorti fréquemment sur les 2 "
"dernières années de tirages."
msgstr ""
"A <strong>hot number</strong> has been drawn frequently over the last 2 "
"years of draws."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:296
msgid ""
"Un <strong>numéro froid</strong> est rarement sorti sur cette même "
"période. Ces numéros ont un retard important."
msgstr ""
"A <strong>cold number</strong> has rarely been drawn over the same "
"period. These numbers have a significant gap."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:297
msgid ""
"L'analyse porte sur les <strong>50 numéros principaux</strong> ET les "
"<strong>12 étoiles</strong>."
msgstr ""
"The analysis covers all <strong>50 main numbers</strong> AND the "
"<strong>12 stars</strong>."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:307
msgid ""
"Les <strong>2 étoiles (1-12)</strong> sont analysées séparément avec leur"
" propre fréquence, écart et catégorie chaud/froid/neutre."
msgstr ""
"The <strong>2 stars (1-12)</strong> are analysed separately with their "
"own frequency, gap and hot/cold/neutral category."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:308
msgid ""
"Le moteur HYBRIDE traite les étoiles comme un espace combinatoire "
"distinct des numéros principaux."
msgstr ""
"The HYBRIDE engine treats stars as a distinct combinatorial space from "
"the main numbers."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:325
msgid ""
"Les données proviennent des <strong>tirages officiels de "
"l'EuroMillions</strong>."
msgstr "The data comes from the <strong>official EuroMillions draws</strong>."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:326
#, python-format
msgid ""
"La base contient <strong>%(total)s tirages</strong> couvrant plusieurs "
"années d'historique."
msgstr ""
"The database contains <strong>%(total)s draws</strong> covering several "
"years of history."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:332
msgid "À quelle fréquence la base est-elle mise à jour ?"
msgstr "How often is the database updated?"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:336
msgid ""
"La base est mise à jour <strong>régulièrement après chaque tirage "
"officiel</strong> (mardi et vendredi)."
msgstr ""
"The database is updated <strong>regularly after each official "
"draw</strong> (Tuesday and Friday)."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:337
msgid ""
"Les grilles sont générées en temps réel à chaque utilisation selon les "
"dernières données disponibles."
msgstr ""
"Grids are generated in real time with each use, based on the latest "
"available data."

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:350
msgid "Quels sont les risques du jeu ?"
msgstr "What are the risks of gambling?"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:354
msgid ""
"Les jeux d'argent et de hasard, dont l'EuroMillions, comportent des "
"risques :"
msgstr "Gambling, including EuroMillions, carries risks:"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:356
msgid "<strong>Pertes financières</strong> : Vous pouvez perdre l'argent misé"
msgstr "<strong>Financial losses</strong>: You can lose the money you stake"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:357
msgid "<strong>Addiction</strong> : Le jeu peut devenir pathologique"
msgstr "<strong>Addiction</strong>: Gambling can become pathological"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:358
msgid "<strong>Impact psychologique</strong> : Stress, anxiété, frustration"
msgstr "<strong>Psychological impact</strong>: Stress, anxiety, frustration"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:359
msgid "<strong>Conséquences familiales</strong> : Endettement, conflits"
msgstr "<strong>Family consequences</strong>: Debt, conflicts"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:361
msgid "<strong>Règles d'or</strong> :"
msgstr "<strong>Golden rules</strong>:"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:363
msgid "Ne jouez jamais plus que ce que vous pouvez vous permettre de perdre"
msgstr "Never gamble more than you can afford to lose"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:364
msgid "L'EuroMillions doit rester un divertissement occasionnel"
msgstr "EuroMillions should remain an occasional form of entertainment"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:365
msgid "N'essayez jamais de \"vous refaire\" après une perte"
msgstr "Never try to \"chase your losses\" after a loss"

#: ui/templates/em/faq.html:372
msgid "Ou trouver de l'aide en cas d'addiction ?"
